        <updateDate>2020-05-08T19:56:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Essential Worker Protection Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Labor to convene an interagency task force to issue guidance on the development and implementation of a comprehensive infectious disease exposure control plan to protect employees identified as having an elevated risk from occupational exposure to the coronavirus (i.e., the virus that causes COVID-19).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
